And finally, she was able to regain a brilliance greater than ever before.

1126
01:13:08,788 --> 01:13:14,788
このお話は決して彼女だけの物語ではありません。
This story is by no means her story alone.

1127
01:13:15,288 --> 01:13:19,788
そう、花屋はいつだってここにある。
Yes, the flower shop is always here.

1128
01:13:20,288 --> 01:13:25,288
あなたの心の中に。
Inside your heart.

